<body>
<!--Banner-->
<section id="banner">
    <div class="banner-text">
        <h1><span>Traum</span><span>Job</span></h1>
          <p>
            Our goal is to make your job search <br>
            an inspiring process <br>
          </p>
        <div class="banner-btn">
            <%= link_to(jobs_path) do %>
              <div><span></span>Find a Job</div>
            <% end %>
            <%= link_to(candidates_path) do %>
              <div><span></span>Find a Candidate</div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!--Nav Bar-->
<div id="sideNav" style="right: -250px;">
    <nav>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="#banner">HOME</a></li>
        <li><a href="#feature">FEATURES</a></li>
        <li><a href="#path">YOUR PATH</a></li>
        <li><a href="#review">OUR REVIEWS</a></li>
        <li><a href="#footer">CONTACT US</a></li>
    </ul>
    </nav>
</div>
<div id="menuBtn">
      <%= image_tag "menu.png", id:"menu" %>
</div>

<!--Features-->
<section id="feature">
<div class="title-text">
<p>FEATURES</p>
<h1>How it works</h1>
</div>
<div class="feature-box">
    <div class="features">
        <h1>Create an Account</h1>
        <div class="features-desc">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-sharp fa-light fa-user"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <p>You can Sign In in our page and have all the benefits as a Job Seeker or even as a future employer!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Look for a Job</h1>
        <div class="features-desc">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <p>You could look for jobs, apply for that unique opportunity, chat with your future employer or even schedule your appoiments</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Post a new job offer</h1>
        <div class="features-desc">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-solid fa-pen-nib"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
                <p>If you have already created your business and need someone on board to help you boost it, this space is also for you!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="features-img">
        <%= image_tag "dream_job2.jpg", class:"features-img" %>
    </div>
</div>
</section>

<!--User Paths-->
<section id="path">
    <div class="title-text">
    <p>YOUR PATH</p>
    <h1>Your options are here!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="path-box">
        <%= link_to jobs_path, class:"links" do %>
        <div class="user-path">
            <%= image_tag "user-jobseeker.jpg" %>
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="path-desc">
                <h3>Find a Job</h3>
                <hr>
                <p>Save and apply for jobs, keep track of your journey with your own calendar and have up-to-date your cvs.</p>
            </div>
        <% end %>
        </div>
        <%= link_to candidates_path, class:"links" do %>
        <div class="user-path">
            <%= image_tag "user-employer.jpg" %>
            <div class="overlay"></div>
            <div class="path-desc">
                <h3>Find a Candidate</h3>
                <hr>
                <p>Find the right match for your company here. Talk to the candidates and schedule meetings in your calendar.</p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>

<!--Reviews-->
<section id="review">
    <div class="title-text">
    <p>OUR REVIEWS</p>
    <h1>What users say about us</h1>
    </div>
<div class="review-row">
    <div class="review-col">
        <div class="reviewer">
            <%= image_tag "reviewer-1.jpg", class:"reviewer-img" %>
            <div class="reviewer-info">
                <h4>John W. <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></h4>
                <small>@johnw</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>After my bootcamp I could not focus on another process. Traumjob secured me my dream job the day I trusted the app!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="review-col">
        <div class="reviewer">
        <%= image_tag "reviewer-2.jpg", class:"reviewer-img" %>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
            <h4>Mery M. <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></h4>
            <small>@merym</small>
        </div>
        </div>
        <p>I was unemployed and desperate. Traumjob helped me to focus, save my process and get a job in a healthy and safe way!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="review-col">
        <div class="reviewer">
        <%= image_tag "reviewer-3.jpg", class:"reviewer-img" %>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
            <h4>Adam L. <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></h4>
            <small>@adaml</small>
        </div>
        </div>
        <p>I was looking for the ideal person for a very important position in my company. The order offered by the app made the way to find him more pleasant and simple.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</section>

